ank  有沒師兄有門路入/請教virtual bank 可否當踏腳石轉入bank同埋點樣入。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/27/virtualbankhongkong/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F27%2Fvirtualbankhongkong%2Flife-tech%2F&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=f33fdbf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/27/virtualbankhongkong/life-tech/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2322255/WeLab%20%E7%8D%B2%E7%AC%AC4%E5%BC%B5%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E7%89%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2322255%2FWeLab%2520%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25AC%25AC4%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2589%258C&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=e944830f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2322255/WeLab%20%E7%8D%B2%E7%AC%AC4%E5%BC%B5%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E7%89%8C</a><br />\nHKMA最近出咗四個vb牌，分別係中銀，渣打，眾安同WeLab，都係呢一個月既事。阿里巴巴同Tencent好似未有住，定reject咗?<br />\n四間都請緊人，好似眾安同WeLab最多job post，樓主可以搵下，入咗vb就唔好返傳統銀行了，畢竟四間都從新build個core banking system，而且vb應該會係第時個trend，無理由仲走返去傳統銀行搞D舊野。<br />\n不過間間都話六至九個月出，但間間都仲請緊人，預左趕deadline要大量OT，我估佢地應該都係用Java為主，但如果個project好趕，你又得2年經，無搞過microservices，可能難D。<br />\nAnyway，祝你好運"},{"pid":"e06610825f4fff9d8b80c103443338268fb4b9e4","tid":1126153,"uid":249527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac88cb7c4eb124651cc3ef187695f5cf9380784a","tid":1126153,"uid":141121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"Virtual Bank呢排好缺人 某幾間大行係咁搵Candidate Non-coder 出手&gt;40k 都幾好市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"新開一間bank，要請好多risk，finance，compliance，同埋好多team都係先請咗manager grade先，所以&gt;40k好正常，甚至有D低，但developer應該都係市價咁請，例如中銀同渣打都係Jardine同PCCW果邊請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d3db23febbdda6700aec850980